{"tid":2178162,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[眾籌] 十月一日 登頭版眾籌","createTime":"2020-08-28T08:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T14:25:24.000Z","uid":217127,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f60de68025325ebab182f472cc8560ea99d4296a","tid":2178162,"uid":217127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"十月一日 又一個悲慘既日子<br />\n<br />\n我地永遠唔會忘記呢一日<br />\n<br />\n我地想借頭版一頁 提醒番大家 <br />\n<br />\n頭版設計如下（呢個係初稿） 有意見可以提出 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cdcyigq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCdcyigq.jpg&h=0985566d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nUp jpg檔 上黎有點低清 <br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲都認同我地理念 可以click落下面條link幫手眾籌 share出去比更多人 多多少少支持 積少成多 十月一日見！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2G2jIK9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2G2jIK9&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=87328421\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2G2jIK9</a>"},{"pid":"c14839c302fbeba6b88ce3fd04adf7e944e91b9e","tid":2178162,"uid":217127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5816cb7fb3a07d48bac538d2dbb69bef1d30a4d7","tid":2178162,"uid":206987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:26:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a5e940bc0f279029be0ad8375487de5ddd76f15f","tid":2178162,"uid":217127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a663707cc2d4155b8877ee4d2ef48bdbc3c4c7f6","tid":2178162,"uid":217127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:27:26.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"14b6e838ad87f2af1867bab69f2d8d053aa2b8c1","tid":2178162,"uid":217127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d2021c35071e15650788255b55a582877173228c","tid":2178162,"uid":217127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:00:4